方伊琪正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分飛燕，其實係一首令德哥真係係70年代中期紅到去美加既代表作<br />\n<br />\n原唱1973 陳浩德、甄秀儀<br />\n原來歌名叫   囑咐話兒莫厭煩 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GIyb7pQIOhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGIyb7pQIOhc&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=7cce280e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GIyb7pQIOhc</a><br />\n<br />\n因為1974年前，香港粵語流行曲都未係真正主流，所以當年一有人出唱片，基本上就會一大堆人翻唱，麗莎、鄭錦昌、尹光當年就係咁，當中以麗莎最少原唱歌，基本上都係翻唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麗莎1974 已經同譚炳文翻唱 囑咐話兒莫厭煩 ，唱片改叫做分飛燕，自此呢首歌就都係叫做分飛燕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hpgqn1o8Hlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHpgqn1o8Hlg&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=217ed3bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hpgqn1o8Hlg</a><br />\n<br />\n德哥當年當然繼續唱、後來就係不停拍住方伊琪唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUwUPjySZ1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHUwUPjySZ1U&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=612281a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUwUPjySZ1U</a><br />\n<br />\n淨係一首歌都咁多版本，呢個現象係當年好盛行，呢d香港廣東歌歷史，我覺得有需要有人留意關注，全部涉及當時社會文化背景，好本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dbef80f7a4a8aadf04444966b161c860259c85","tid":242919,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br